<h2>Start driving more AI referral traffic</h2>
<p>This will likely include a bit of trial and error. Figure out what‚Äôs most effective for your site in bringing in AI traffic (and eventually <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-lead-generation">leads</a>), and then do more of that.</p>
<p>While organic and paid traffic from search engines like Google aren‚Äôt going anywhere, it doesn‚Äôt hurt to incorporate some of these tactics into your strategy to help you capture traffic from these often-used AI tools (and keep up with how Google continues to expand <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/google-ai-mode">AI use in results</a>).</p>
